text: Cadeau Kelley (born 9 May 1986) is a retired Liberian long jumper. He finished sixth at the 2006 African Championships. He also competed at the 2007 All- Africa Games without reaching the final. His personal best jump is 8.00 metres, achieved April 2009 in Ypsilanti.
